---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Callout from '../components/Callout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="About Us | Maine Dispensary Guide" 
  description="Learn about our mission to provide the most accurate, transparent, and encouraging resources for Maine cannabis entrepreneurs."
  heroImage="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1511497584788-876760111969?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=1200&h=400"
>
  <div class="article-header">
    <h1>About Maine Dispensary Guide</h1>
    <p class="lead">Empowering Maine's founders to build compliant, thriving cannabis businesses.</p>
  </div>

  <section>
    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
    <Callout title="Our Philosophy" type="passion">
      We believe that the next generation of Maine's economy is being built by small business owners like you. Our goal is to demystify the "Legal Maze" so you can focus on the craft and the community you love.
    </Callout>
    <p>Maine Dispensary Guide exists to help entrepreneurs navigate the complex process of opening and operating a cannabis dispensary in Maine. We provide comprehensive, accurate, and up-to-date information on licensing, regulations, compliance, and business operations.</p>
  </section>
  
  <section>
    <h2>Why Maine?</h2>
    <p>Maine's cannabis market has grown significantly since the passage of recreational use in 2016 and the launch of retail sales in 2020. With a supportive regulatory environment and growing demand, Maine presents genuine opportunities for cannabis entrepreneurs.</p>
    <p>However, navigating the licensing process, understanding regulations, and building a compliant operation can be challenging. We're here to simplify that journey.</p>
  </section>
  
  <section>
    <h2>What We Offer</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>License Guides</strong> - Step-by-step instructions for obtaining your Maine dispensary license</li>
      <li><strong>Regulatory Information</strong> - Current rules and requirements for cannabis businesses</li>
      <li><strong>Business Resources</strong> - Templates, tools, and recommendations for dispensary operations</li>
      <li><strong>Industry Insights</strong> - Market analysis and opportunities in Maine's cannabis sector</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="success-stories">
    <h2>Founder Success Stories</h2>
    <p>Read about the entrepreneurs who are building the Maine cannabis legacy.</p>
    <div class="story-grid">
      <a href="/founders/maine-cannabis-founder-coastal-shop" class="story-card">
        <h3>The Coastal Boutique</h3>
        <p>How community trust built a seaside brand.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/founders/maine-cannabis-founder-rural-cultivator" class="story-card">
        <h3>The Rural Leap</h3>
        <p>From Tier 1 craft grower to retail storefront.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/founders/maine-cannabis-founder-portland-flagship" class="story-card">
        <h3>The Portland Flagship</h3>
        <p>Scaling a premier brand in the big leagues.</p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <section class="disclaimer">
    <h2>Legal Disclaimer</h2>
    <p>The information provided on this website is for informational purposes only and does not constitute legal, financial, or business advice. Cannabis regulations change frequently, and you should always consult with qualified professionals, including attorneys and accountants, when making business decisions.</p>
  </section>
  
  <section>
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions or suggestions? Reach out to us.</p>
    <p><a href="mailto:info@mainedispensaryguide.com">info@mainedispensaryguide.com</a></p>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .article-header {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .lead {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  section {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }
  
  section h2 {
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
  }
  
  .disclaimer {
    background: #fff3cd;
    border: 1px solid #ffc107;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
  }

  ul {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  li {
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .success-stories {
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .story-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .story-card {
    background: white;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 1.5rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }

  .story-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    border-color: var(--color-primary);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
  }

  .story-card h3 {
    margin-top: 0;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .story-card p {
    margin-bottom: 0;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
  }
</style>
